name: Watching all the Universe with my soulmate
description: “...You have someone to go to the cinema, theater, restaurant. You probably have someone to marry. But you have no one to look at the stars with. Someone said well that we all dig in the mud, but some of us also look at the stars... ”(S. Rodionov) |||| This art was created about those who have a soulmate. They can look together not only on the stars, but on a thousand other wonderful phenomena in the Universe. |||| Music video with generative elements, 1200 x 834, 30s.
